  <brief_title>Exparel Transversus Abdominis Plane Block vs Intrathecal Analgesia In Colorectal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exparel Transversus Abdominis Plane Block vs Intrathecal Analgesia In Colorectal Surgery: A Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
